data.description: Welcome to this exquisite full brick estate nestled on the prestigious east Anniston mountain. This remarkable property boasts a spacious 4 bedroom, 3 full bath, and 2 half bath layout, spanning over an impressive 4700 square feet of luxurious living space. As you step inside, prepare to be captivated by the beautiful grand entryway, inviting you into a world of elegance and comfort. Every detail has been carefully considered, with updated bathrooms, fresh paint, and new flooring enhancing the overall appeal and charm of this magnificent home.With a generously sized basement spanning over 2000 square feet, the possibilities are endless. Create your dream entertainment area, a home gym, or even a private office - the choice is yours. Situated on a large lot of nearly 2 acres, this property offers the perfect blend of privacy and space.
